May we create unapologetically.

Express all that we are.

Explore all that it means to be human.

Love fearlessly.

Your greatest compass within.

Your greatest guide a little whisper and intuitive hit.

It's always beautiful coming into collaboration with another that you trust.

Bringing together different perspectives gained from different life experiences and energy types.

It's always beautiful expanding your perspective with the illumination of another.

But always remember.

You know your truth better than anyone else.

You know what is right for you.

Because your truth will always feel freeing in your body.

(even if sometimes it's mixed with some fear - there will be excitement and freedom!)

Gone are the days where we give our power away to a special few that are ‘connected to the Divine’.

You are the Divine.

Trust yourself.

node.text:
How has Cancer Season been treating you? 🌊🌙

As we said under the gorgeous Cancer New Moon earlier in the month, Cancer is both the parent and the child.

It asks us to embody both archetypes within ourselves.

It asks us to nurture ourselves.

Take care of ourselves – just as we would a child.

It asks us to remember our worth and show up for ourselves in alignment with that worth.

Before Cancer Season comes to a close and we head into the fire of Leo...

Ask yourself – what does it mean for you to show up for yourself?

node.text:
Fun astrology basics!

Astrology houses represent areas and aspects of the human experience.

Each house/area is shaped and coloured by the zodiac sign it holds (at the time of your birth) and any planets that may reside in them.

The same is when planets are moving through your houses, and how they are in relationship/angles to other planets - your experience of Life will be coloured and shaped by that movement.

Remember, you as a divine being are infinite and limitless.

Your natal chart brings structure to your limitless nature.

Allowing each of us to be expressed and to experience ourselves in the most unique and magical way!

Truly a magical system to explore the self through.

We have 5 astrology readings available - all viewing the self and human experience through a different lens. 

To find out more or get a reading for yourself, click the link in our bio! x

node.text:
Free Angel Numbers Cheat Sheet via our highlight ‘FREE ANGEL NUMBERS’! 
🌸🖤✨

If you find yourself seeing 999 often and are ready to uncover the energy and messages within these numbers, read on! 👼

Life is always guiding us, supporting us, and holding us with the deepest love – our job is to let ourselves receive.

This guidance comes in many many forms, like Tarot, Astrology, experiences, people, music – but one of the easiest and quickest would have to be by numbers.

We are surrounded by numbers constantly, with the time, on social media, documents, license plates and so much more – what could be easier for our angels?!

Numerology is a sacred science dating back thousands upon thousands of years where deep deep wisdom can be found and remembered.

9, 999, 9999 speaks to the expanding awareness of your mind.

Your awareness is expanding and your compassion is deepening.

Take this awareness and compassion and turn it inward to release all that isn’t love – thoughts, beliefs, energies.

Take this awareness and compassion and look at what really matters to you, what matters in your life, in your heart, in the heart of humanity?

And with that, let yourself release the rest. 

If you want a full Angel Numbers Cheat Sheet – visit our highlight ‘FREE ANGEL NUMBERS’ to download! 🖤

Know that the Universe is always communicating, supporting and guiding you.

May this Cheat Sheet help you recognize and align with the flow of the Universe. xx

node.text:
You as a divine being are infinite and limitless.

Astrology is not a tool to box you in or limit you in any way.

Your unique natal chart brings structure to the limitless self, allowing for a beautiful expression that is ultimately you.

It is not stagnant. You are not boxed in. And your chart reflects this.

Our astrology readings are infused with the intention of bringing conscious awareness to the unique flow of your Souls energy.

And how to work in harmony with that energy to open the doors to your deepest fulfilment and highest expression.

Your natal chart can reveal, bring awareness to, and guide us in many areas of our lives.

It is our opportunity to connect with our Souls intentions and most aligned desires for this lifetime.

Like a beautiful little roadmap where we can see all that our Souls envisaged coming into this life.

We're incredible lucky to have this art, this insight, this understanding.

If you would like to know more about our readings, or are ready to get one for yourself - the link is in our bio! 🖤

node.text:
Still swimming in the beauty of the recent Cancer New Moon 🌙

Encouraging the beautiful healing that can be found in emotion.

In nurturing ourselves.

In holding ourselves.

In letting Life in. 

Inner healing. Deep nurturing.

A beautiful surrender. 

If you feel guided - take a moment to feel into where your heart is pulling you right now. 

Breathe calm into your body. 

Breathe safety into your body.

To fully open to this human experience is courageous. 

Thank you for being here. Thank you for choosing again and again and again to be here. 

To experience all it means to be human.

To crack open. To live fully.
